  "detailed_description": "Shred space ships with lasers, plasma, and missiles in an epic online multiplayer space battle with Allspace.  Up to 100 players can blast each other online.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Features:</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>First Person Space Pilot<br></li><li>Online Multiplayer with support for up to 100 players<br></li><li>Highly Optimized (150+ FPS on a modern gaming PC)</li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Online Multiplayer</h2>Allspace supports up to 100 players at a time.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Gameplay</h2>Allspace currently supports Deathmatch mode.  Join the Steam Discussion forums for Allspace to suggest new games modes and features.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Supports Keyboard, Mouse, Game Controller, and Joysticks</h2>All keyboard, mouse, game controller, and joystick controls can be re-mapped to suit each player's unique play style.",
